ant;\n    }\n\n    .footer {\n        width: 100% !important;\n    }\n}\n\n@media only screen and (max-width: 500px) {\n    .button {\n        width: 100% !important;\n    }\n}', 1, NULL, '2020-04-13 09:24:37', '2020-04-13 09:24:37');

